{"tid":1600582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動】929 集合時間 唔係唔知下話 ?","createTime":"2019-09-28T16:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T23:37:19.000Z","uid":279356,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a429d18c12567b270ddc6506c0c313206bef1514","tid":1600582,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:13:49.000Z","msg":"感謝文宣原創者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下係 929 四大活動<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hj2ih4V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhj2ih4V.jpg&h=2fb9b682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NUUTRpW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNUUTRpW.jpg&h=b5277e0e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">9.29 全球反極權大遊行</span></strong></span><br />\n以「全球連線，對抗極權」為口號，反送中運動將於 2019 年 9 月 29 日發起「9.29 全球反極權大遊行」，號召各國民眾在當天一起上街，支持香港反送中五大訴求。據悉，現已有包括台灣在內至少 10 個國家的網友響應。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">929 遊行路線安排</span></strong></span><br />\n為聲援香港反送中運動，台灣有多個民間團體發起「929 台港大遊行&mdash;撐港反極權」遊行活動，遊行路線將從立法院外出發，行經西門町一帶再返回集合點，呼籲香港特區政府和平面對示威者，並盡快回應香港抗爭者的五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n香港方面，929 全球反極權大遊行路線從銅鑼灣 SOGO 軒尼詩道出發，遊行至金鐘政府總部。遊行時間為 9 月 29 日下午 14:30 集合，15:00 起步，遊行衣著 Dress Code 則為黑色衣物。<br />\n<br />\n除香港和台灣外，響應 929 遊行的國家還有日本、英國、澳洲、德國、義大利、法國、加拿大、荷蘭、波蘭、愛爾蘭、烏克蘭、以及愛沙尼亞；當中有較多華人居住的國家如美國、澳洲，更有多個城市響應。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">【INFO】929 全球反極權大遊行</span></strong></span><br />\n日期：2019年9月29日(星期日)<br />\n時間：14:30集合，15:00起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣 SOGO 軒尼詩道為起點，金鐘政府總部為終點<br />\n遊行衣著 Dress Code：黑色衣物<br />\n<br />\n【NearSnake】原文網址＠ <a href=\"https://www.nearsnake.com/event-pro/29th-sept-global-anti-totalitarianism-march-2019/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nearsnake.com%2Fevent-pro%2F29th-sept-global-anti-totalitarianism-march-2019%2F&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=0338ba2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nearsnake.com/event-pro/29th-sept-global-anti-totalitarianism-march-2019/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zq8EM07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZq8EM07.jpg&h=b8a7e32e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>9.29 荃灣區中學生罷課集會</strong></span></span><br />\n為響應「10.1 三罷行動」，荃灣區學界擬於 2019 年 9 月 29 日發起「9.29 荃灣區中學生罷課集會」，呼籲區內中學生當天前往荃灣公園集會，重申反修例「五大訴求缺一不可」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">929 集會進駐荃灣公園</span></strong></span><br />\n9.29 荃灣區中學生罷課集會將於 9 月 29 日下午 14:30 至 19:00 在荃灣公園舉行。較早前，荃灣區學界曾舉行「9.20 荃灣區中學人鏈行動」，區內十多間學校當日下午 18:00 築起聯校人鏈，重申「五大訴求缺一不可」。荃灣人鏈之路以荃灣官立中學起點，沿途經福來村、路德圍、荃灣站連至石圍角，另一端則連至愉景新城，有超過一千位參與這次人鏈行動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【INFO】929 荃灣區中學生罷課集會</span></strong></span><br />\n日期：2019年9月29日(星期日)<br />\n時間：下午14:30至19:00<br />\n地點：荃灣公園<br />\n<br />\n【NearSnake】原文網址＠ <a href=\"https://www.nearsnake.com/event-pro/29th-sept-tsuen-wan-school-strike-2019/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nearsnake.com%2Fevent-pro%2F29th-sept-tsuen-wan-school-strike-2019%2F&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=4d7d8ae7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nearsnake.com/event-pro/29th-sept-tsuen-wan-school-strike-2019/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">【人道救援誓師大會】</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LMPHKP0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLMPHKP0.jpg&h=05666f2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fF8EM3m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfF8EM3m.jpg&h=bee50e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">【重現新疆集中營行動】</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/atvWPm2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FatvWPm2.jpg&h=7703949d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B2s4vhUFXPG/?igshid=kkfpwt7nkf0x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB2s4vhUFXPG%2F%3Figshid%3Dkkfpwt7nkf0x&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=6ff1b30f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB2s4vhUFXPG%2F%3Figshid%3Dkkfpwt7nkf0x&h=d77a0791\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B2s4vhUFXPG/?igshid=kkfpwt7nkf0x</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/salih_hudayar/status/1175436966688673797?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsalih_hudayar%2Fstatus%2F1175436966688673797%3Fs%3D21&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=6348538a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsalih_hudayar%2Fstatus%2F1175436966688673797%3Fs%3D21&h=045c86cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/salih_hudayar/status/1175436966688673797?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"0de0c11608a9c9cc02906a2e6411309ba8726d20","tid":1600582,"uid":241742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:44:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac460744e8ba81f90e773e1a69544a7631f8eea","tid":1600582,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:45:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ac28e2769a5602390e94e1431f2b11fe8852bcde","tid":1600582,"uid":203332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:47:42.00